    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! Honestly, this ride has been such a joy to own and it's still in really wonderful shape. It runs like a dream and has been super dependable for me. I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you! It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and reliability. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels behind the wheel. Drop me a message if you have any questions!",
