    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This Porsche Cayman S (987.1) is a mechanically sound example of the mid-engine 3.4L flat-six platform. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain delivers linear power through the VarioCam Plus system. The chassis remains sharp with no detectable bushing play, and the braking system utilizes four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers for superior modulation. Recent service includes a complete cooling system refresh and a new set of high-performance tires. While the finish shows light road patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a tactile and communicative driving experience for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 29500.0,
