    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a balanced blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with the bodywork showing only the minor, superficial marks consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the seats provide excellent support with minimal wear, and all onboard technology\u2014from the premium sound system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the car has been meticulously maintained with a documented service history, ensuring the engine runs quietly and the gear transitions are seamless. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a thorough brake inspection, meaning it is ready for the road immediately. It has been kept in a smoke-free environment and primarily garaged, preserving the integrity of the materials. This is a dependable, high-quality car that delivers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
