    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 straight-six mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example has had the critical subframe reinforcement completed and the VANOS system overhauled with Besian components to ensure valvetrain longevity. The rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance, and a recent valve adjustment has the engine idling smoothly with peak induction note. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by refreshed bushings and a factory M Variable Differential Lock that provides exceptional corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain integrity and throttle response remain razor-sharp, making this a quintessential driver\u2019s car.",
